# Optional: enables real-time live data from the BALLDONTLIE FIFA World Cup API.
# Without it, the app runs fully on the keyless openfootball feed (near-real-time)
# plus computed standings. Get a free key at https://www.balldontlie.io
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your key. The EXPO_PUBLIC_ prefix is what
# makes it available in the client bundle.
EXPO_PUBLIC_BALLDONTLIE_KEY=
